dc_title_s: Nova Poloniae delineatio; ex officina et sumptibus Iudoci Hondii.
dc_description_s: Relief shown pictorially. Upper and lower border with town views. Side borers with include examples of local costumes. From "Atlantis maioris appendix" by Jan Jansson, 1630. 1 map; 35 x 49 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
dc_creator_sm: Jansson, Jan, 1588-1664.,Jansson, Jan, 1588-1664. Atlantis Maioris Appendix, 1630.,Hondius, Jodocus, 1594 or 1595-1629, cartographer.,Vignaud, Henry, 1830-1922, former owner.
